projects.name: Air Quality Index Analysis in Delhi
projects.description: Conducted a comprehensive analysis of the Air Quality Index (AQI) in Delhi, a city known for its significant air pollution challenges. The project involved gathering real-time and historical air quality data from government sources, analyzing trends, and identifying key contributors to air pollution in the region.

projects.name: Heart Disease Prediction using Machine Learning
projects.description: Developed a predictive model to assess the likelihood of heart disease based on medical attributes including age, sex, blood pressure, cholesterol levels, and other relevant factors. Utilized Python and machine learning libraries such as Scikit-learn and Pandas for data preprocessing, model training, and evaluation. Deployed the model using Flask, enabling real-time predictions via a web interface. Conducted thorough analysis and visualization of data insights using Matplotlib and Seaborn.
